Could you meet me here with either of these options? If so, would be so excited to sign the offer this week!

𝐏𝐮𝐭 𝐢𝐭 𝐚𝐥𝐥 𝐭𝐨𝐠𝐞𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫:

